{"id": "1517237354069233896", "channel_id": "1300659718653476925", "type": 0, "author_id": "1288649877903118417", "author_name": "ellerabudo", "author_bot": false, "content": "Por ela já ter tanto destaque faz mais sentido tentar dar um pouquinho de destaque pra quem nunca tem", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T18:39:34.117000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1517238142082613399", "channel_id": "1300659718653476925", "type": 19, "author_id": "1247682399513612392", "author_name": "lordfelipe0827_59720", "author_bot": false, "content": "Aí é que tá o problema:\nA Doll tem destaque, mas o problema é que mal sabemos ou temos noção de nada sobre ela", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T18:42:41.994000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1288649877903118417"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1517237354069233896", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1517238274819887196", "channel_id": "1300659718653476925", "type": 0, "author_id": "1247682399513612392", "author_name": "lordfelipe0827_59720", "author_bot": false, "content": "Diferente do ogler que ganhou um mergulho, a Doll não ganhou nada", "timestamp": "2026-06-18T18:43:13.641000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
